Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.44,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滴落的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:45.41,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转变为勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:48.46,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.46,0:00:51.54,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挥舞着天使的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:04.34,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚持到底 不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:09.49,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直坚持的东西 一定有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:13.07,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just try again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:15.57,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃离黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.57,0:01:19.34,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:24.43,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来一直都在等待我们大显身手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.14,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跃过天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:30.22,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越大海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.17,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:36.92,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使的飞吻吧（you can try！）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:43.14,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去开始永不结束的冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:48.59,OP*,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到永远 永无止境
